ugate addition of a nucleophile to an α,β-unsaturated system).\n\nFor the mechanistic classification, the best label is: **Michael addition** or **conjugate addition**.\n\nGiven the task asks for mechanistic_class and reaction_center, and the expected output schema is \"mechanistic_label\", I should provide the mechanistic class label.\n\nThe mechanistic class is: Michael addition (conjugate addition)\n\nLet me finalize with the most appropriate label."
